# Documentation policy

- ALL research, architecture, and knowledge artifacts for this repo → `docs/src/architecture/` (NOT IDE knowledge bases)
- `.vox` and `.tsx` code blocks in `docs/src/` must use `{{#include}}` from `examples/golden/` OR be annotated `// vox:skip`
- Do NOT edit derived ignore files (`.cursorignore`, `.aiignore`, `.aiexclude`) — edit `.voxignore` and run `vox ci sync-ignore-files`
- Do NOT read or modify `docs/src/archive/` for new feature work
- New doc pages must include `category`, `status`, `last_updated`, and `training_eligible` frontmatter
